Author: Qiang Liu [aut, cre],
    Mingrui Zhang [aut],
    Yuan Liu [aut]
Maintainer: Qiang Liu <leo.liu3@emory.edu>
Description: Implements bias-corrected generalized propensity score matching
    for estimating average treatment effects in observational studies with two
    or more treatment groups. The package estimates generalized propensity
    scores, matches across all treatment levels, optionally applies
    treatment-specific outcome adjustment, and provides overlap and covariate
    balance diagnostics. Multinomial logistic propensity scores and linear
    outcome models provide the baseline workflow. Flexible learners and tuning
    integrations are optional; the XGBoost and ranger backends are experimental
    and remain under active testing.
